5044			; | SETTAPE ( port gap samples hpulse lpulse high low -- )   Set parameters for tape support | DONE 
5044			; | | port - Device address port; default is Device A on 00h 
5044			; | | samples - How many sample cycles to count pulses 
5044			; | | gap - Gap period counter; default is 250 
5044			; | | hpulse - Count of pulses for 1; default is 6 
5044			; | | lpulse - Count of pulses for 0; default is 2 
5044			; | | high - High bit period counter; default is 150 
5044			; | | low - Low bit period counter; default is 50 
